cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use OrthoSec in your work, please cite it as below."
title: "OrthoSec: The AI Security Architect"
abstract: >-
  OrthoSec is an open-source AI security scanner. Deterministic detectors map
  findings in AI/LLM applications to the OWASP LLM Top-10 and MITRE ATLAS, and a
  grounded intel layer translates them into business risk and compliance exposure.
type: software
authors:
  - family-names: Kumar
    given-names: Vikas
repository-code: "https://github.com/cloudivian-org/OrthoSec"
url: "https://github.com/cloudivian-org/OrthoSec"
license: Apache-2.0
keywords:
  - ai-security
  - llm-security
  - owasp-llm-top-10
  - mitre-atlas
  - static-analysis
  - prompt-injection
